responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "3D14C94B4A291B8CC39C429A48F9A756", "Absolutely! The bandits may infest the hills, but it is still the rightful territory of the Kaelar Empire. If you hope to join the Thanacite rush to those hills, then you will have to go speak to Captain Eudoxia in Lionhold. ")
